{"about_the_game":"Lead your robot team to liberate the world from the evil CCP.<br />\r\nBuild your robots team by different body parts: helm, head, eye, ear, mouth, chest, back,  abdomen, pelvis,  shoulder, forearm,  thigh, calf, foot, attack skill, weapon. <br />\r\nEach part color is also editable by picking on a color picker.<br />\r\nPick 5 passive traits out of 20 traits for each robot.  It is possible to combine different trait make a robot to taunt enemy like a tank,  a damage dealer,  or an enchanter.<br />\r\nFor the battle system, it is different from most strategy game, attack and counter attack happen same times, and attack can be cancelled by another attack depend on the attack type. It creates more uncertainty.<br />\r\nThis is a single player game without online function, but your robot team can be save in a text file and share with friends, and you can fight your friends team by loading their loading robot text file.<br />\r\nYou can create your map by map editor, and share with friends.<br />\r\nThe battle can be played in traditional manual mode, or fully auto like auto chess.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289770/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1592695012","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289770/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1592695012","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289770/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1592695012","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289770/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1592695012","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"Lead your robot team to liberate the world from the evil CCP.<br />\r\nBuild your robots team by different body parts: helm, head, eye, ear, mouth, chest, back,  abdomen, pelvis,  shoulder, forearm,  thigh, calf, foot, attack skill, weapon. <br />\r\nEach part color is also editable by picking on a color picker.<br />\r\nPick 5 passive traits out of 20 traits for each robot.  It is possible to combine different trait make a robot to taunt enemy like a tank,  a damage dealer,  or an enchanter.<br />\r\nFor the battle system, it is different from most strategy game, attack and counter attack happen same times, and attack can be cancelled by another attack depend on the attack type. It creates more uncertainty.<br />\r\nThis is a single player game without online function, but your robot team can be save in a text file and share with friends, and you can fight your friends team by loading their loading robot text file.<br />\r\nYou can create your map by map editor, and share with friends.<br />\r\nThe battle can be played in traditional manual mode, or fully auto like auto chess.","developers":["Shitman497"],"genres":[{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Strategy","id":"2"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289770/header.jpg?t=1592695012","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":256785358,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256785358/movie480.mp4?t=1589442382","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256785358/movie_max.mp4?t=1589442382"},"name":"Auto 4","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/256785358/movie.293x165.jpg?t=1589442382","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256785358/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1589442382","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256785358/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1589442382"}},{"highlight":true,"id":256787853,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256787853/movie480.mp4?t=1591355264","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256787853/movie_max.mp4?t=1591355264"},"nam